_json.description: It doesn't matter where you live in this world of ours, it's great to get outdoors. If the sun is too hot, get under a tree. If the weather is too cold, huddle around the fire pit. Of course, some nice, comfortable outdoor furniture will help. Here's a selection of inspiring ideas to get you started. Got a favourite? Â  Click on any image to start lightbox display.
